window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Build Harem. Grind Hard. Level Fast. </p> <p>Sam has been deemed a dark lord by the Game Masters, and now everyone in Rebirth Online is gunning for him. To make matters worse, an overzealous NPC paladin has been resurrected to destroy Sam and his demon sons. </p> <p>To win this one, Sam might have no choice but to embrace the power of the Dark Throne. </p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
